race.comment: Looks a good assignment for the promising mare BEDTIME ANGEL (9). Winner at this trip two back then scored again last time at Sandown Lakeside. Down in weight and should be finishing on hard. IMMORTAL STAR (14) has found winning form third-up and should be at top now. Won this class latest and drawn for cover. Among the chances again. SHAALUTE (3) placed in higher grade two back then was below best in the latest. Looks well placed here with the claim and gets a chance to atone. RUE DE ROYALE (1) was game in defeat fresh then not far away last time. Ready to win and with the claim looks a top chance to find best form. HEDONIST (11) improved sharply off the fresh-up run to score last time with ease over the border. This is a tougher assignment but drops in weight and will give a sight at odds.
